      • convertPackage

        private static TestPackage convertPackage(CodePackage codePackage,
                                          TestParent testParent,
                                          TemporaryModel tmpModel)
        Static method to convert a given CodePackage to a TestPackage and adds it to the given TestParent.
        Parameters:
        codePackage - the CodePackage to be converted.
        testParent - the TestParent to which to converted TestPackage should be added, can be TestRepresentation of TestPackage.
        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel to add the converted TestPackages to
        Returns:
        the converted TestPackage
